name: //Grunge Dreams// World full of Nothing
description: After left nothing behind, no one alive and the ghost of the last war she started to experience different kind of emotional rutines: The melancholia, the gloom, the dream, and quite often the desire to find someone. The sea is the only place trying to keep the mankind memories after their annihilation and the trace of the war down in the blue deep ocean but that never will be possible, no one is alive. //Unknown IA mother, possibly self-destructed//
